  Variant: Magellan  |  Family: Dark  |  Bg Hue: ~234 deg
  Tagline: Magellan corporate indigo - "Vision in Action", deep navy with a
  bright indigo accent drawn from the post-MeTS-acquisition rebrand.

  Engineering note: the 7 functional accents (Cyan, Green, Orange, Pink,
  Purple, Red, Yellow) and the extended Blue slot are byte-identical to the
  shipped Dark family band so accent-tint switching keeps its uniform
  Oklab-L* behaviour and clears WCAG AA. The brand identity is carried by
  the navy Background / Surface and the indigo Accent. Every gated pair
  (Accent / Success / Warning / Error / Info vs Background, and each
  accent-tint source vs Background) clears WCAG AA 4.5:1 with margin.
  See NOTICE.
